General.Name: Fenix Resources Ltd
General.Description: Fenix Resources Limited engages in the exploration, development, and mining of mineral tenements in Western Australia. The company operates in two segments: Iron Ridge Project and Trucking Joint Venture. Its flagship property is the 100% owned Iron Ridge Iron Ore project located in Western Australia. The company was formerly known as Emergent Resources Limited. Fenix Resources Limited was incorporated in 2007 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
